iated to the high sensitivity\nof transient grating spectroscopy, make their combination a unique tool to\nprobe vibrational dynamics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Mar 2014 05:12:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
